title: Disneyland's 2017 Half Marathon Theme Revealed | Letty B | Y93
text:
Disneyland's 2017 Half Marathon Theme Revealed posted by Letty B - A post shared by runDisney (@rundisney) on Feb 21, 2017 at 9:15am PST 
Source: Instagram 
run Disney lovers it's time to start planning your attire! It has been announced that the Disneyland Half Marathon Weekend will be entirely Pixar themed. 
The runners are encouraged to channel their favorite Pixar characters. Check out the individual theme for each event: Kids Races - "Up!"
